4. Attack Graph

An attack graph shows multiple possible paths.

Example:

Internet
   │
   ▼
Web App
  / \
 /   \
API  Admin Portal
 |        |
 ▼        ▼
Database  Active Directory

An attacker may have several routes to reach the target.


