7. Security Control Mapping

Every attack step should have a corresponding defense.

Attack Stage	Security Control

Phishing	Email Security
Credential Theft	MFA
SQL Injection	Parameterized Queries
Prompt Injection	Input Validation + Guardrails
Data Exfiltration	DLP
Privilege Escalation	Least Privilege


The goal isn't just to understand attacks—it is to identify where defenses should be strengthened.


